    "asOf": "2018-07-11",
    "date": "2018-08-08T23:44:52Z",
    "text": "Allied Burden Sharing Report Act of 2018\n\nThis bill directs the Department of Defense to submit an annual report to Congress describing:\n\n each allied nation's annual defense spending, its contributions to military or stability operations in which the United States participates, and limitations it places on such contributions' use; and actions taken by the United States or by other countries to minimize such limitations."
